Omnisource Technologies was founded in 2006 on the principle that great teams can change the world. Today, we work with clients ranging from edgy startups to multi-billion dollar enterprises, who value a long-term solutions approach to solving software development needs. While most of the team is currently working remotely.
 Job Summary
 We are looking for software engineers from Romania with a good grasp of programming fundamentals, and solid knowledge of Golang for a web & mobile (Android&IOS) application for cleaning services. The app is live in the US at the moment. Technologies used in the project are Golang and Angular.
 What you need
  Software engineering experience;
Confident skills in developing server applications in Golang;
Strong knowledge of relational databases (PostgreSQL);
Strong knowledge of microservice architecture;
Strong knowledge gRPC/ RESTful / GraphQL APIs;
Familiar with messaging systems such as RabbitMQ, and Kafka;
